      <title>《信贷周刊》：即将到来的并购浪潮将为债务银行家带来福音</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/coming-m-a-wave-will-be-a-boon-for-debt-bankers-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[并购银行家们希望唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫能带来比之前预期更多的新交易。债务承销商也可能从中获益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/coming-m-a-wave-will-be-a-boon-for-debt-bankers-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
